        <abstract>
            <p>Has read a German author’s exposition of CD’s theory.</p>
            <p>Believes "missing link" between higher mammals and man consists of a race of "speaking monkeys" – akin to Africans – who pollute blood of better race and impede civilisation.</p>
        </abstract>
